# Domain Layer Guide

Domain models capture the core business concepts. They are Pydantic models and contain no framework or persistence logic.

```python
class User(BaseModel):
    id: int | None = None
    username: str
    email: EmailStr
    hashed_password: str
```

Domain converters (`src/domain/converters/`) are stateless helpers that map external representations to these entities.

